\c 8
\s UJesu usilisa umlephero
\p
\v 1 Kwathi esehlile entabeni, amlandela amaxuku amakhulu;
\v 2 njalo khangela, olobulephero weza wamkhonza wathi\x + Mark. 1.40-44. Luka 5.12-14.\x*: Nkosi, aluba uthanda ungangihlambulula\x + 9.18; 15.25; 18.26; 20.20. Mark. 5.6; 15.19. Joha. 9.38.Mat. 14.33; 28.9,17. Seb. 10.25.\x*.
\v 3 UJesu waseselula isandla, wamthinta, wathi: Ngiyathanda, hlambuluka\x + 8.15. 20.34.\x*. Njalo ubulephero bakhe bahle bahlanjululwa.
\v 4 UJesu wasesithi kuye: Khangela ungatsheli muntu\x + 9.30; 12.16; 16.20; 17.9. Mark. 1.25,34; 3.12; 5.43; 7.36; 8.26,30. Luka 5.14; 9.21.\x*; kodwa hamba, uziveze kumpristi, unikele umnikelo uMozisi awulayayo\x + Levi 14.2,3,4,10,21,22. Mat. 5.23.\x*, kube yibufakazi kubo\x + 10.18; 24.14. Mark. 6.11; 13. 9. Luka 9.5.\x*.
\s Ukusiliswa kwenceku yenduna
\p
\v 5 Kwathi uJesu esengenile eKapenawume, kweza kuye induna yekhulu imncenga\x + Luka 7.1-10.\x*,
\v 6 yasisithi: Nkosi, inceku yami ilele endlini yome umhlubulo, isebuhlungwini obukhulu\x + Dute. 13.1-3. Jer. 14.14; 23.9,14-17,21,25. Mat. 24.4,5,11,24. Mark. 13.5,22. Luka 21.8. 2 Pet. 2.1-3. 1 Joha. 4.1.\x*.
\v 7 UJesu wasesithi kuye: Mina ngizakuza ngiyisilise.
\v 8 Induna yekhulu yasiphendula yathi: Nkosi, kangifanele ukuthi ungene ngaphansi kophahla lwami\x + Luka 15.19,21.\x*; kodwa kuphela khuluma ilizwi, njalo inceku yami izasiliswa.
\v 9 Ngoba lami ngingumuntu ongaphansi kwamandla, ngilamabutho ngaphansi kwami; njalo ngithi kuleli: Hamba, beselihamba; lakwelinye: Woza, beselisiza; lencekwini yami: Yenza lokhu, njalo ikwenze\x + Hlab. 107.20.\x*.
\v 10 Kwathi uJesu esezwile wamangala, wathi kwabalandelayo: Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Angitholanga ukholo olungaka ngitsho lakoIsrayeli\x + 9.2.\x*.
\v 11 Njalo ngithi kini: Abanengi bazakuza bevela empumalanga lentshonalanga\x + Isa. 2.2,3; 11.10; 60.1-3. Mal. 1.11. Luka 13.29. Seb. 10.45; 11.18; 14.27; 15.9. Roma 10.12; 15.9-12. Gal. 3.14,28. Efe. 3.6. Gen. 12.3.\x*, bahlale loAbrahama loIsaka loJakobe, embusweni wamazulu\x + 26.29. Luka 22.30.\x*;
\v 12 kodwa abantwana bombuso\x + 13.38. 21.43.\x* bazaphoselwa emnyameni ongaphandle\x + 22.13; 25.30.\x*; lapha kuzakuba khona ukukhala lokugedla amazinyo\x + 13.42,50; 22.13; 24.51; 25.30. Luka 13.28. 2 Pet. 2.17. Juda 13.\x*.
\v 13 UJesu wasesithi enduneni yekhulu: Hamba, futhi kakube kuwe njengoba ukholiwe. Inceku yakhe yasisiliswa ngalelohola.
\s Uninazala kaPetro labanye abagulayo bayasiliswa
\p
\v 14 Kwathi uJesu engene endlini kaPetro\x + Mark. 1.29-34. Luka 4.38-40.\x*, wabona uninazala\x + 1 Kor. 9.5.\x* elele njalo ebulawa luqhuqho\x + 8.6. Luka 16.20. Mat. 9.2. Mark. 7.30. Isam. 2.22.\x*.
\v 15 Wasebamba isandla sakhe, njalo uqhuqho lwamyekela; wasesukuma, wabancedisa\x + 8.15. 20.34.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Kwathi sekuhlwile baletha kuye abanengi ababengenwe ngamadimoni; wasekhupha omoya ngelizwi, wasilisa bonke abagulayo\x + 4.24.\x*;
\v 17 ukuze kugcwaliseke okwakhulunywa nguIsaya umprofethi ukuthi: Yena wathatha ubuthakathaka bethu, wazithwala izifo \add zethu\x + Isa. 53.4. 1 Pet. 2.24.\x*\add*.
\s Ukumlandela uJesu
\p
\v 18 Kwathi uJesu ebona amaxuku amakhulu emhanqile, walaya ukuthi bachaphele ngaphetsheya\x + Mark. 4.35. Luka 8.22.\x*.
\v 19 Kwasekusondela umbhali othile wathi kuye: Mfundisi, ngizakulandela loba kungaphi lapho oya khona.
\v 20 UJesu wasesithi kuye: Amakhanka alemilindi, lenyoni zezulu izidleke; kodwa iNdodana yomuntu kayila lapho engaqamelisa ikhanda khona\x + Luka 9.57-60.\x*.
\v 21 Omunye wabafundi bakhe wasesithi kuye: Nkosi, ngivumela ukuthi ngiqale ngiyengcwaba ubaba\x + 1 Kho. 19.20.\x*.
\v 22 Kodwa uJesu wathi kuye: Ngilandela, uyekele abafileyo bangcwabe ababo abafileyo.
\s Ukuthuliswa kwesiphepho
\p
\v 23 Kwathi esengenile emkhunjini, abafundi bakhe bamlandela\x + Mark. 4.36. 5.17. Luka 8.22,37.\x*.
\v 24 Njalo khangela, kwavuka isiphepho esikhulu olwandle, okungangokuthi umkhumbi wagutshuzelwa ngamagagasi; kodwa yena wayelele.
\v 25 Basebesondela abafundi bakhe bamvusa, besithi: Nkosi, sisindise, siyabhubha!
\v 26 Wasesithi kubo: Lesabelani, lina abokholo oluncinyane\x + 6.30.\x*? Wasesukuma wakhuza imimoya lolwandle; kwasekusiba khona ukuthula okukhulu\x + Hlab. 65.7.\x*.
\v 27 Kodwa abantu bamangala, besithi: Ngonjani lo, ukuthi lemimoya lolwandle kumlalele?
\s Ukukhutshwa kwabomoya ababi
\p
\v 28 Kwathi esefikile ngaphetsheya elizweni lamaGergesi\x + Gen. 15.21. Dute. 7.1. Josh. 3.10; 24.11. Mark. 5.1. Luka 8.26.\x*, bamhlangabeza ababili\x + Mark. 5.2. Luka 8.27.\x* ababengenwe ngamadimoni bephuma emangcwabeni, belolaka kakhulu, okungangokuthi kwakungekho odlula ngaleyondlela\x + 4.24.\x*;
\v 29 njalo khangela, bamemeza besithi: Silani lawe\x + 2 Sam. 16.10.\x*, Jesu, Ndodana kaNkulunkulu\x + 14.33.\x*? Uze lapha yini ukusihlupha kungakafiki isikhathi?
\v 30 Kwakukhona khatshana labo umhlambi wengulube ezinengi usidla.
\v 31 Amadimoni asemncenga, esithi: Uba usikhupha, sivumela ukuthi sihambe singene emhlanjini wengulube.
\v 32 Wasesithi kuwo: Hambani. Esephumile angena emhlanjini wengulube; futhi khangela, umhlambi wonke wengulube waphaphatheka eliweni usiya olwandle, zafela emanzini.
\v 33 Abazelusayo basebebaleka, basebesiya emzini babika konke, lezin\add daba\add* zababengenwe ngamadimoni\x + 4.24.\x*.
\v 34 Njalo khangela, umuzi wonke waphuma ukumhlangabeza uJesu; bathi bembona, bancenga ukuthi asuke emikhawulweni yakibo\x + Dute. 5.25-27. 2 Sam. 6.9. 1 Kho. 17.18. Luka 5.8. Seb. 16.39.\x*.